'''Thallastam''' was a [[Chondathan]] [[human]] man of [[the Vast]] of the 6th century [[DR]]. He was a famous expert in magical swords, a practitioner of the [[Sublime Way]], and a [[Jade Phoenix mage]].{{Cite web/Class Chronicles: Crusaders, Swordsages, Warblades|}}
